WEBVTT

00:00:40.920 --> 00:00:41.719
Zhu Yihai

00:00:42.079 --> 00:00:43.719
I just wanted to help you

00:00:44.039 --> 00:00:45.280
I just wanted to tell you

00:00:45.280 --> 00:00:47.640
It's not just Qian Huilian and Wei Wei who can help you

00:00:47.640 --> 00:00:49.079
I, Qiao Lili, can too

00:00:49.079 --> 00:00:50.679
Lili, you're not worthless

00:00:50.679 --> 00:00:53.119
Everything you've done means a lot to me

00:00:53.600 --> 00:00:55.439
Lili, you know what?

00:00:56.479 --> 00:00:58.439
I'm not Zhu Yihai

00:00:59.079 --> 00:01:00.560
I'm Zhu Chaoyang

00:01:08.799 --> 00:01:10.640
You're the only one who cares what I eat every day

00:01:10.640 --> 00:01:11.879
and what I wear every day

00:01:12.599 --> 00:01:14.000
When I'm hurt

00:01:15.799 --> 00:01:17.799
you're the one I want to see the most

00:01:20.280 --> 00:01:22.599
You make me feel cared for

00:01:22.599 --> 00:01:24.680
And how wonderful it is to be looked after

00:01:28.400 --> 00:01:29.719
Zhu Yihai, stop talking

00:01:31.280 --> 00:01:32.079
Lili

00:01:35.519 --> 00:01:36.319
I love you

00:01:40.239 --> 00:01:41.560
If I could

00:01:43.319 --> 00:01:45.680
I wish I could be the man you imagine me to be

00:01:48.959 --> 00:01:50.719
Do you remember your dream?

00:01:53.879 --> 00:01:55.159
Me?

00:01:55.560 --> 00:01:57.359
What dream could I possibly have?

00:01:58.400 --> 00:02:00.719
Just don't do anything stupid. Stay safe

00:02:02.799 --> 00:02:04.640
So this is what a Heart flutter feels like

00:02:05.239 --> 00:02:07.319
It's the first time I've ever felt Warmth

00:02:09.840 --> 00:02:10.719
Warmth

00:02:12.759 --> 00:02:13.560
Zhu Yihai

00:02:14.879 --> 00:02:17.520
Aren't you the one who gave me Warmth too?

00:02:18.479 --> 00:02:19.319
After that incident

00:02:19.319 --> 00:02:20.439
everyone was saying

00:02:20.439 --> 00:02:22.280
that I, Qiao Lili, am a tainted woman

00:02:24.520 --> 00:02:26.439
Only you were willing to Fight injustice for me

00:02:29.199 --> 00:02:30.439
But you shouldn't have lied to me

00:02:30.800 --> 00:02:32.120
I could've lived forever

00:02:32.120 --> 00:02:33.280
in that bleak world

00:02:33.280 --> 00:02:34.319
Barely surviving

00:02:34.879 --> 00:02:37.439
But you can't fool me with fake Warmth

00:02:38.000 --> 00:02:39.639
It's Addictive

00:02:40.159 --> 00:02:41.360
If you look down on me

00:02:41.360 --> 00:02:42.919
you shouldn't have helped me in the first place

00:02:43.520 --> 00:02:46.120
You shouldn't have made me think of you every second

00:02:46.639 --> 00:02:48.439
When did I ever look down on you?

00:02:48.439 --> 00:02:50.360
Then how did you treat me, Zhu Yihai?

00:02:53.919 --> 00:02:55.319
You pushed me away

00:02:55.719 --> 00:02:56.520
I love you

00:03:01.560 --> 00:03:02.560
Do you know how much courage

00:03:02.560 --> 00:03:04.360
I had to muster up that night?

00:03:04.719 --> 00:03:06.560
A living, breathing Qiao Lili like me

00:03:06.560 --> 00:03:08.840
can never compare to that Qian Huilian

00:03:11.960 --> 00:03:12.759
Fine

00:03:14.039 --> 00:03:14.919
Since that's how it is

00:03:17.759 --> 00:03:19.800
it's time for me to bow out

00:03:21.680 --> 00:03:22.479
Zhu Yihai

00:03:23.240 --> 00:03:24.639
Give me the Transfer Agreement

00:03:25.919 --> 00:03:27.400
and the Giant Wood Group is yours

00:03:28.000 --> 00:03:29.080
What do you want?

00:03:31.159 --> 00:03:32.400
Everything Long Xiao has

00:03:33.680 --> 00:03:35.439
This is my final gift to you

00:03:36.159 --> 00:03:37.680
You call this a gift?

00:03:39.719 --> 00:03:41.120
A massive Giant Wood Group

00:03:41.120 --> 00:03:42.560
can't even buy your love?

00:03:43.199 --> 00:03:45.560
Do you know what'll happen if Long Xiao and his backers

00:03:45.560 --> 00:03:47.000
get hold of Aimin Street?

00:03:47.000 --> 00:03:47.800
I know

00:03:48.919 --> 00:03:50.000
But I don't care about them

00:03:50.000 --> 00:03:51.159
The one I care about is you

00:03:51.159 --> 00:03:52.240
I care about you too

00:03:53.319 --> 00:03:55.199
But if I'm not with Qian Huilian

00:03:55.759 --> 00:03:57.280
there's no future for me

00:03:57.479 --> 00:03:58.719
Qian Huilian again

00:04:00.960 --> 00:04:01.759
Fine

00:04:03.560 --> 00:04:04.879
I'll step aside for you two

00:04:07.479 --> 00:04:08.919
Give me the Transfer Agreement

00:04:10.599 --> 00:04:12.039
I'm taking back this gift

00:04:13.960 --> 00:04:15.280
If you're not willing

00:04:17.279 --> 00:04:18.240
I can help you

00:04:31.000 --> 00:04:31.879
What's this?

00:04:31.959 --> 00:04:32.920
That's all public funds.

00:04:32.920 --> 00:04:33.519
Embezzlement of public funds

00:04:33.519 --> 00:04:34.800
will land you in jail.

00:04:34.800 --> 00:04:35.720
Let's see where you can run now.

00:04:35.800 --> 00:04:36.480
Dali.

00:04:36.480 --> 00:04:38.040
Throw that bag down to me.

00:04:38.439 --> 00:04:38.959
Here.

00:04:46.439 --> 00:04:47.839
Well done, Qiao Lili.

00:04:49.040 --> 00:04:51.360
You were already setting a trap back then.

00:04:51.360 --> 00:04:52.439
I just thought at the time

00:04:52.439 --> 00:04:53.920
that if this got you involved,

00:04:53.920 --> 00:04:56.160
I could use this photo to clear your name.

00:04:56.439 --> 00:04:57.759
But I never expected, Zhu Yihai...

00:04:59.199 --> 00:05:00.079
You forced my hand.

00:05:00.639 --> 00:05:01.680
What do you want?

00:05:01.959 --> 00:05:02.759
First,

00:05:03.399 --> 00:05:05.480
hand over the Aimin Street Transfer Agreement,

00:05:06.959 --> 00:05:07.720
or else,

00:05:08.000 --> 00:05:10.560
I'll turn in this photo of Xiong Dali stealing

00:05:11.000 --> 00:05:12.680
and let him rot in jail.

00:05:12.680 --> 00:05:14.519
Long Xiao is the one who set up Xiong Dali.

00:05:14.519 --> 00:05:15.319
I know.

00:05:16.680 --> 00:05:17.920
But that photo doesn't show that.

00:05:19.959 --> 00:05:23.399
Embezzlement of public funds is no small charge.

00:05:24.519 --> 00:05:25.800
It was you.

00:05:26.839 --> 00:05:29.680
I didn't expect you were the one who framed my father.

00:05:31.920 --> 00:05:34.120
How could I have fallen for you?

00:05:36.279 --> 00:05:38.519
I won't use the future of every worker at the factory

00:05:38.839 --> 00:05:40.000
to make a deal with you.

00:05:41.160 --> 00:05:43.240
Hand over the Aimin Street Transfer Agreement,

00:05:43.560 --> 00:05:44.360
or else,

00:05:44.560 --> 00:05:47.000
I'll turn in this photo of Xiong Dali stealing

00:05:47.600 --> 00:05:48.800
and let him rot in jail.

00:05:48.800 --> 00:05:50.040
And this recording

00:05:50.519 --> 00:05:52.560
will be evidence of you threatening others.

00:05:53.720 --> 00:05:55.319
The evidence you destroyed about Secretary Yu before

00:05:55.319 --> 00:05:56.439
is still on my phone.

00:05:57.160 --> 00:05:58.639
I'll hand it to the police tomorrow too.

00:05:58.920 --> 00:06:01.800
If you did wrong, you must face the consequences.

00:06:02.360 --> 00:06:04.839
Zhu Yihai, you say you love me

00:06:04.839 --> 00:06:05.839
while keeping your guard up against me.

00:06:05.839 --> 00:06:07.240
I'm not guarding against you.

00:06:07.720 --> 00:06:09.920
This is my way of telling you,

00:06:10.360 --> 00:06:11.319
Qiao Lili,

00:06:11.319 --> 00:06:12.639
wrong is wrong.

00:06:12.879 --> 00:06:14.399
We have to face it bravely.

00:06:23.160 --> 00:06:25.120
Every cop in the city is looking for me now.

00:06:26.199 --> 00:06:27.800
Come turn yourself in with me tomorrow.

00:06:29.800 --> 00:06:30.600
Don't worry.

00:06:32.959 --> 00:06:34.720
I, Zhu Chaoyang, won't leave you.

00:06:49.319 --> 00:06:51.800
Qiao Lili agreed to turn herself in with me.

00:06:52.759 --> 00:06:54.480
The hospital also notified me

00:06:55.120 --> 00:06:56.040
that my mother woke up.

00:07:17.519 --> 00:07:18.800
You scared me!

00:07:18.920 --> 00:07:19.839
What are you doing?

00:07:23.360 --> 00:07:24.160
Huilian.

00:07:24.680 --> 00:07:25.519
Happy birthday.

00:07:32.399 --> 00:07:33.600
What's this about, Zhu Yihai?

00:07:34.120 --> 00:07:35.839
I'm celebrating your birthday.

00:07:36.480 --> 00:07:38.199
All these years you've been working overtime,

00:07:38.439 --> 00:07:40.160
or sticking up for other people.

00:07:41.639 --> 00:07:43.079
How come now you suddenly remember

00:07:43.079 --> 00:07:44.079
to celebrate my birthday?

00:07:46.120 --> 00:07:47.680
You actually remembered our promise.

00:07:50.920 --> 00:07:52.199
Only now do I realize

00:07:53.560 --> 00:07:55.199
how much Zhu Yihai loves you.

00:07:55.759 --> 00:07:57.439
You're not going after your Qiao Lili?

00:07:57.800 --> 00:07:59.759
Without you, there's no me.

00:07:59.759 --> 00:08:00.920
Hurry up and make a wish.

00:08:00.920 --> 00:08:02.680
Otherwise it'll burn my hand.

00:08:04.199 --> 00:08:07.959
Happy birthday to you.

00:08:10.360 --> 00:08:10.920
Huilian.

00:08:10.920 --> 00:08:11.839
Happy birthday.

00:08:12.279 --> 00:08:13.560
Happy birthday.

00:08:21.319 --> 00:08:22.639
You prepared this too?

00:08:23.800 --> 00:08:24.959
Today's New Year's Day.

00:08:25.759 --> 00:08:28.680
I was just going to say we set this up specially.

00:08:34.600 --> 00:08:35.399
Huilian.

00:08:36.000 --> 00:08:36.879
It's New Year's Day.

00:08:37.360 --> 00:08:38.799
Can you promise me one thing?

00:08:39.279 --> 00:08:40.080
Go on, say it.

00:08:47.960 --> 00:08:48.960
Wait for me to come back.

00:09:03.600 --> 00:09:04.519
Are you sure?

00:09:05.159 --> 00:09:06.200
Of course.

00:09:07.000 --> 00:09:08.960
Someone has to take the fall for this.

00:09:09.440 --> 00:09:10.360
Zhu Yihai.

00:09:10.360 --> 00:09:12.559
Long Xiao's ledger has been turned in.

00:09:12.799 --> 00:09:14.480
Secretary Yu behind him got arrested too.

00:09:28.279 --> 00:09:29.600
After Secretary Yu went down,

00:09:29.960 --> 00:09:32.480
private investors are willing to back our factory.

00:09:32.679 --> 00:09:33.679
Our factory's saved.

00:09:33.679 --> 00:09:34.759
You can definitely do it.

00:09:34.759 --> 00:09:37.159
A top student like you can definitely manage the factory well.

00:09:38.039 --> 00:09:38.759
Dahai.

00:09:39.759 --> 00:09:41.879
My eye surgery has been scheduled too.

00:09:42.200 --> 00:09:43.200
Don't worry.

00:09:43.360 --> 00:09:44.480
You jerk.

00:09:47.879 --> 00:09:49.000
I'm sorry, everyone.

00:09:56.639 --> 00:09:57.840
I'm turning myself in.

00:10:06.080 --> 00:10:06.960
Bro.

00:10:09.440 --> 00:10:11.200
Be a man.

00:10:16.720 --> 00:10:17.519
It's done.

00:10:22.960 --> 00:10:23.759
Huilian.

00:10:26.120 --> 00:10:27.120
I'm sorry.

00:10:27.799 --> 00:10:31.159
You might not see me for a while.

00:10:37.519 --> 00:10:38.399
I'll wait for you.

00:10:43.799 --> 00:10:44.600
I'm off.

00:10:45.799 --> 00:10:46.879
See you later, Brother Hai.

00:10:48.000 --> 00:10:48.960
Zhu Yihai!

00:10:49.240 --> 00:10:50.200
Zhu Yihai!

00:10:51.000 --> 00:10:52.080
Zhu Chaoyang!

00:10:54.080 --> 00:10:55.679
Zhu Chaoyang!

00:11:02.360 --> 00:11:04.519
My brother may have wronged your sister,

00:11:04.639 --> 00:11:06.559
but I can't let you touch my brother.

00:11:06.960 --> 00:11:07.559
Brother Hai, you guys go first.

00:11:08.120 --> 00:11:08.759
These small fry,

00:11:08.759 --> 00:11:09.279
I can handle them.

00:11:09.279 --> 00:11:10.480
Hurry, go!

00:11:11.480 --> 00:11:13.039
If I weren't sharp,

00:11:13.080 --> 00:11:14.320
I'd think you really had a Heart flutter.

00:11:14.320 --> 00:11:15.240
Just you wait.

00:11:15.360 --> 00:11:17.960
No way we're letting him take the factory.

00:11:18.000 --> 00:11:18.799
Come on.

00:11:18.879 --> 00:11:20.080
Let's dance.

00:11:24.440 --> 00:11:26.559
I'm at least head of security, you know.

00:11:26.840 --> 00:11:27.600
Pin him down!

00:11:33.039 --> 00:11:33.600
Get him!

00:11:35.320 --> 00:11:38.279
Your good days end today.

00:11:38.639 --> 00:11:39.559
Who the hell are you?

00:11:40.279 --> 00:11:41.399
Your nemesis.

00:11:41.799 --> 00:11:42.960
Yihai!

00:11:42.960 --> 00:11:43.759
Hang in there!

00:11:43.840 --> 00:11:45.240
Yihai!

00:11:47.519 --> 00:11:48.919
What could possibly happen to you, Zhu Yihai?

00:11:49.399 --> 00:11:50.519
You've got money for massage parlors,

00:11:50.519 --> 00:11:51.639
but no money to pay me back, huh?

00:11:52.879 --> 00:11:53.879
What's between us

00:11:53.879 --> 00:11:55.639
isn't something so easily settled.

00:11:56.240 --> 00:11:57.879
That sixty thousand yuan debt

00:11:57.879 --> 00:11:59.279
was purely an excuse.

00:11:59.759 --> 00:12:01.000
Who's your brother?

00:12:07.240 --> 00:12:08.799
See you around.

00:12:30.519 --> 00:12:31.320
Huilian.

00:12:33.519 --> 00:12:34.320
What's wrong with you?

00:12:35.559 --> 00:12:36.440
Thank God.

00:12:36.440 --> 00:12:37.559
Mom, you're not dead!

00:12:37.919 --> 00:12:39.399
What are you talking about, you silly kid?

00:12:39.639 --> 00:12:40.559
Mom...

00:12:40.639 --> 00:12:42.399
I had such a long, long dream.

00:12:46.240 --> 00:12:46.720
Let go.

00:12:46.720 --> 00:12:47.480
I don't want to.

00:12:47.879 --> 00:12:48.240
Let go.

00:12:48.240 --> 00:12:48.960
I don't want to.

00:12:48.960 --> 00:12:49.759
Let go!

00:12:51.840 --> 00:12:52.919
Why are you so excited?

00:12:54.879 --> 00:12:56.759
Does Mom look pretty today?

00:12:56.759 --> 00:12:57.679
Yeah, pretty.

00:12:57.679 --> 00:12:58.360
Beautiful, huh?

00:12:58.360 --> 00:12:59.159
Beautiful.

00:12:59.480 --> 00:13:02.840
What if I put on these little shades?

00:13:03.440 --> 00:13:04.240
Super stylish!

00:13:04.240 --> 00:13:05.159
Super stylish, huh?

00:13:05.399 --> 00:13:06.360
Let's go, get in the car.

00:13:06.360 --> 00:13:06.840
Let's go.

00:13:07.720 --> 00:13:10.159
Come on, let's pick up your dad from prison.

00:13:43.240 --> 00:13:44.399
What are you here for?

00:13:44.840 --> 00:13:46.759
Picking this kid up from school.

00:13:52.600 --> 00:13:53.440
It wasn't easy.

00:13:53.799 --> 00:13:54.720
You're finally out.

00:13:54.799 --> 00:13:56.120
Tonight, Seafood Tower.

00:13:56.120 --> 00:13:56.879
I'll set it up.

00:13:56.879 --> 00:13:58.399
To hell with Seafood Tower.

00:13:59.399 --> 00:14:01.000
Didn't you say your wife's dumpling filling is delicious?

00:14:01.559 --> 00:14:03.159
Let's just go to your place for some dumplings.

00:14:03.440 --> 00:14:04.159
Alright.

00:14:05.639 --> 00:14:07.440
I'll go pick up my grandson first,

00:14:08.120 --> 00:14:09.559
then bring him to see you.

00:14:11.000 --> 00:14:11.799
Sure.

00:14:12.279 --> 00:14:13.279
See you tonight.

00:14:13.480 --> 00:14:14.080
Okay.

00:14:19.200 --> 00:14:20.000
You little devil.

00:14:22.759 --> 00:14:24.200
Get your butt over here already.

00:14:30.000 --> 00:14:31.759
Aren't you cold, dressed like that?

00:14:39.080 --> 00:14:40.759
What's with all the mushy stuff?

00:14:41.039 --> 00:14:42.080
What, you got a problem with it?

00:14:43.320 --> 00:14:44.320
Chaoyang, come here.

00:14:45.639 --> 00:14:46.440
Dad.

00:14:48.799 --> 00:14:49.600
Speak up.

00:14:50.600 --> 00:14:51.279
Dad.